ception);\\n                }\\n            }\\n        }, \\\"jedis-test-server\\\");\\n        serverThread.setDaemon(true);\\n        serverThread.start();\\n        return acceptedConnection;\\n    }\\n\"}]}}], \"api\": \"openai-responses\", \"provider\": \"OCA\", \"model\": \"gpt-5.5\", \"usage\": {\"input\": 5948, \"output\": 1478, \"cacheRead\": 11776, \"cacheWrite\": 0, \"totalTokens\": 19202, \"cost\": {\"input\": 0, \"output\": 0, \"cacheRead\": 0, \"cacheWrite\": 0, \"total\": 0}}, \"stopReason\": \"toolUse\", \"timestamp\": 1777803868480, \"responseId\": \"resp_035c3093fce308820169f7225cd12c819c928e2a5cf65a5bff\"}, \"toolResults\": [{\"role\": \"toolResult\", \"toolCallId\": \"call_sYx0FVv9XhrW6TSXZcQ7Dda8|fc_035c3093fce308820169f7226e2c54819c8b625c6d6e9c87eb\", \"toolName\": \"edit\", \"content\": [{\"type\": \"text\", \"text\": \"Successfully replaced 1 block(s) in tests/src/redis.clients/jedis/4.4.0/src/test/java/redis_clients/jedis/JedisTest.java.\"}], \"details\": {\"diff\": \"     ...\\n 298     private static CompletableFuture<Void> acceptSingleConnection(ServerSocket serverSocket) {\\n 299         CompletableFuture<Void> acceptedConnection = new CompletableFuture<>();\\n 300         Thread serverThread = new Thread(() -> {\\n 301             try (Socket socket = serverSocket.accept()) {\\n+302                 socket.setSoTimeout(5_000);\\n+303                 socket.getOutputStream().write(bytes(\\\"+OK\\\\r\\\\n+OK\\\\r\\\\n\\\"));\\n+304                 socket.getOutputStream().flush();\\n 302                 acceptedConnection.complete(null);\\n-303                 socket.getInputStream().read();\\n+306                 while (socket.getInputStream().read() != -1) {\\n+307                     // Drain startup commands until the Jedis client closes the connection.\\n+308                 }\\n 304             } catch (IOException exception) {\\n 305                 if (acceptedConnection.isDone() || serverSocket.isClosed()) {\\n 306               